    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Vesicular Herpetic Lesions\nNonspecific Flu-like Illness\nLymphadenitis\nSite of inoculation - pain, numbness, itching\nCNS - poor coordination, respiratory depression\nEncephalitis - late stage of the disease",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
